data.description: If you’re looking for an established home that is move-in ready and full of charm, this is the one! This all brick, 3BR/1B listing features hardwood floors throughout with tile in the kitchen, bath and utility room. The eat-in kitchen has granite countertops with stainless appliances and the accent wall in the living room will wow your guests. The home is located conveniently off Memorial Drive and has a fenced back yard that will be the perfect place for your spring and summer cookouts. With endless investment potential it won’t last long so schedule your showing today!
